#. <section class="sutta" id="sn7.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn7.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Arahantavagga"
msgstr "1. The Perfected Ones"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn7.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Bilaṅgikasutta"
msgstr "4. With Bhāradvāja the Bitter"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.352"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.4:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, in the Bamboo Grove, the "
"squirrels’ feeding ground."

# For bilangika, see my note on AN 3.39. Once again, this is a descriptive epithet, the comm’s explanation misses the point.
msgctxt "sn7.4:1.2"
msgid "Assosi kho bilaṅgikabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo:"
msgstr "The brahmin Bharadvāja the Bitter heard a rumor to the effect that:"

msgctxt "sn7.4:1.3"
msgid ""
"“bhāradvājagotto kira brāhmaṇo samaṇassa gotamassa santike agārasmā "
"anagāriyaṃ pabbajito”ti kupito anattamano yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā tuṇhībhūto ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi."
msgstr ""
"“A brahmin of the Bharadvāja clan has gone forth from the lay life to "
"homelessness in the presence of the ascetic Gotama!” Angry and displeased he "
"went to the Buddha and stood silently to one side."

msgctxt "sn7.4:1.4"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā bilaṅgikassa bhāradvājassa brāhmaṇassa cetasā "
"cetoparivitakkamaññāya bilaṅgikaṃ bhāradvājaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Then the Buddha, knowing what Bhāradvāja the Bitter was thinking, addressed "
"him in verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.4:2.1"
msgid "“Yo appaduṭṭhassa narassa dussati,"
msgstr "“Whoever wrongs a man who has done no wrong,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.4:2.2"
msgid "Suddhassa posassa anaṅgaṇassa;"
msgstr "a pure man with a spotless record,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.4:2.3"
msgid "Tameva bālaṃ pacceti pāpaṃ,"
msgstr "the evil backfires back on the fool,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.4:2.4"
msgid "Sukhumo rajo paṭivātaṃva khitto”ti."
msgstr "like fine dust thrown upwind.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.4:3.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, bilaṅgikabhāradvājo brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When he said this, the brahmin Bhāradvāja the Bitter said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn7.4:3.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe …"
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! …” …"

msgctxt "sn7.4:3.3"
msgid "abbhaññāsi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn7.4:3.4"
msgid "Aññataro ca panāyasmā bhāradvājo arahataṃ ahosīti."
msgstr "And Venerable Bhāradvāja became one of the perfected."
